node.text: Raging wildfires have erupted around the world in countries such as Italy, USA, Turkey, Spain, France, Cyprus, Finland, Lebanon, Canada & Greece just to name a few. There’s also been detrimental flooding in Italy, Belgium, Netherlands, Germany & China. Hail bigger than avocados have hauled down in northern Italy causing large damage.
